# Frontend Conventions

## Hooks

Business logic in `src/hooks/` — not in components. Main hook: `useChat`.

## Types

`src/types/api.ts` mirrors `backend/app/schemas/chat.py`. Use `ApiError` from `src/lib/api.ts`.

## Styling

Tailwind CSS v4 only. shadcn/ui in `src/components/ui/`.
Chat layout: `flex flex-col h-dvh`; messages scroll; input fixed at bottom.

## Components

- `MessageBubble` — markdown for assistant
- `SourceBadges` — citations from `ChatResponse.sources`
- `ErrorBoundary` wraps `ChatPanel` in `App.tsx`

## Dev proxy

`/api` → `http://localhost:8000` in `vite.config.ts`.
